== Availability ==
The Centaur is available in all Argon Shipyards.  The Pirate variant, however, can only be acquired through boarding operations. 

'''It is also worth noting''' that with the release of Albion Prelude, you can acquire the Centaur relatively early, by completing just a few starting missions in the Albion plot (do-able in a decently-fitted M3, such a Mamba Raider, or even smaller ships with better piloting skills). 

